text: kulula.com was a low-cost carrier from South Africa. It had a partnership with British Airways. The name kulula means easily in the Zulu language. kulula suspended operations on june 2022 in the same year it was placed at liquidation ==References== Category:Low-cost airlines Category:Airlines of South Africa Category:Johannesburg Category:2001 establishments in Africa Category:2000s establishments in South Africa
